text:
Morning [redacted_name], I hope you are doing well. I noticed you have returned to my site LuxLifeMiamiBlog.com looking at Coral Gables real estate. We will be delighted to assist you. Please let me know if you would like a chat about the market, different communities and the best real estate options of the moment.
Looking forward to hearing from you!
Best
[redacted_name]
Cell: +1.305.508.0899
www.luxlifemiamiblog.com
trans:

귀하의 소식을 기다리고 있겠습니다!
감사합니다.
